issue: CSV export fails with 504 Gateway Timeout when exporting large reports
resolution: Implemented chunked CSV export with pagination (50k rows per chunk)

issue: Export to CSV stalls at 99% and never completes for big datasets
resolution: Raised export timeout to 180s and added background job queue

issue: Downloading CSV results in an empty file for large queries
resolution: Added streaming backpressure and temporary files for large exports

issue: CSV export throws 'stream ended unexpectedly' error
resolution: Optimized SQL with covering indexes on date and org_id

issue: Export job to CSV gets canceled due to size limits
resolution: Enabled server-side compression and incremental export windows

issue: Large CSV export fails with 'ERR_STREAM_WRITE_AFTER_END'
resolution: Implemented chunked CSV export with pagination (50k rows per chunk)

issue: CSV download returns 500 when selecting more than 100k rows
resolution: Raised export timeout to 180s and added background job queue

issue: Export to CSV completes but file is corrupted for large reports
resolution: Added streaming backpressure and temporary files for large exports

issue: CSV export fails intermittently during peak hours
resolution: Optimized SQL with covering indexes on date and org_id

issue: CSV export to S3 times out for multi‑month ranges
resolution: Enabled server-side compression and incremental export windows
